reviewText: Ive been searching this movie for my grandmother for a while. Now I found it for her and she is very happy.
Was glad this was still available. Would have been nice if the quality was a bit better, but overall very happy with the video.
I  have not open this VHS my VHS player broke, but I am sure and hope is in good condition.  I love this movie I was like 9 years old when I went to see it.  I am hoping to get a VHS soon!
it was exactly what I expected. I had been searching for this item for years. I would highly recommend it!
I love this movie! I have been trying to find it for so long and I am so glad that Amazon had it. Worth every penny.

If you've ever seen Menudo when you grew up this is a movie for you. It will bring back chilhood memories from Puerto Rico and how much fun it was to see Menudo back when you where a kid.  Buy it and you will see that is was worth it.  Plus this is a grat way to show your kids what YOU used to like when you wher a kid.  Enjoy with the entire family.
I WAS  SO YOUNG WHEN MENUDO APPEARS IN MY LIFE HIS MUSIC AND DANCE SAVE TO BE IN DRUGS , THANKS ALL MENUDO MEMMBERS

I remember this movie when I was a little girl.  I love MENUDO then and I still love them now.  This movie is a true collecter's item for those who acknowledge MENUDO as being the first ever spanish rock 'n roll band.
